title: F the FDA & Don Benigno Cigars
itunes:title: F the FDA & Don Benigno Cigars
description: Jose Ramos from Don Benigno Cigars joins us as we compare the Don Benigno Natural vs Maduro cigar. The FDA has their nose in Premium Cigars, and we tell you why it's not going to be good. This and lots more on The Cigar Authority.
